# claude-memory vault excludes (explore-76oc §4.1, D1 — sandbox-validated).
# Whitelist: ignore everything, then re-include ONLY <slug>/memory/**.
# Applied via `git -c core.excludesFile=<this>` so the vault stages only the
# memory tier over the shared ~/.claude/projects work-tree, leaving the 2 GB of
# transcripts untracked. Do NOT edit without re-running bootstrap's
# "only */memory/** staged" assertion.
/*
!*/
*/*
!*/memory/
!*/memory/**
